instruction: Create a list of items needed if a family has a pet dog.
output:
1. Dog food 
2. Dog treats 
3. Grooming tools 
4. Dog bed 
5. Dog toys 
6. Training accessories 
7. Collar and leash 
8. Waste bags 
9. Grooming shampoo and conditioner 
10. Nail clippers 
11. Veterinary appointments
12. Crate 
13. Water bowl 
14. Food bowl 
15. Dog bowl mat 
16. Pet identification tags 
17. Pet insurance 
18. Flea and tick treatments 
19. Pet waste scoop
